item.title: 2 new community Covid-19 patients linked to family cluster at Tampines Street 11 HDB block
item.description:
July 11, 2020 12:36 AM

SINGAPORE - Two of the new community coronavirus patients announced on Friday (July 10) are family members of a known family cluster at a Tampines Housing Board block where nine people were earlier found to be infected.
